metadata.name: The Street Raider
metadata.description:
The Street Raider lives in the cyber city, where everyone is afraid of because she has guns and weapons.

And because of her form, she keeps robbing most of the money as you can see the money is lying on the road. Because people ran away leaving money when they were withdrawing money from the machine.

She want to be free from money slavery. Because there is only one verb that matters: money
